728129f-a.text:
Utopia Parkway, west side, at Jewell Avenue, showing the farmland and buildings which belonged to Boylan in 1873. L. H. Alden was the owner in 1891 and Jacob Foster in 1909.

P. L. Sperr View 1: April 6, 1927
View 2: March 31, 1927
